msg: Add validate-files.py, a python pre-commit hook-script that runs commands and
rejects commits if the command does not exit with a 0 exit code.

author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Praveen Agrawal "Implementing Try-Catch while Adding UiLabel Resources" https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-5119

In OrderServices.java in method 'sendOrderNotificationScreen (Line :2427) a try catch block must be there surrounding to Adding UiLabel resources to map. So that if any of the resource is not found then rest of the code does not fail.
